When Overgrown Husk enters the battlefield, you may put a land card from your hand onto the battlefield tapped.
Compleat {1}{G}{G} [i]({1}{G}{G}, Exile this card from your graveyard: Create a token that’s a copy of it, except it’s a Phyrexian artifact in addition to its other types. Activate only as a sorcery.)[/i]
